data.title: Laughs and Brews at Fatty's Beer Works! A Live Stand Up Comedy Event!
data.meta_description: Join us for an evening of touring stand-up comedy and local brews at Fatty's Beer Works!
data.text:
Laughs on the Go presents a unique night out featuring the finest that comedy has to offer, paired with Fatty's Beer Works signature brews!

We've hand-picked some of our favorite stand-up comics from around the country to perform secret, one-night-only shows at special venues across the country

Brand New Lineup of Comedians every Show!

We bring the best comedians to local breweries for evenings that keeps the draughts flowing, and the laughs coming. We provide the absolute funniest in comedy entertainment, with our comics having credits at top festivals, on TV, and in major national and international clubs. All you need to do is come ready to laugh!

Tickets:$15.00 Advance, $20.00 Same Day/At The Door

Show Starts at 7:30pm! Arrive early to grab a drink (or two)and pick your seat! Seating is first come, first serve.

Connect with us on Facebook by following "Laughs in the Go" for a chance to win a beer flight for you and a friend on the evening of the show! (Winner messaged on day of show at 12:00 PM)
